INSERT INTO `news_types` VALUES (5,'Economy','Stay updated with the latest financial trends, market insights, and global economic developments. From stock market updates to policy changes, get in-depth analysis and breaking news that impact businesses, investments, and your financial well-being.','2024-12-23 17:55:39','2024-12-23 17:55:39'),(6,'Politics','Stay updated with the latest developments in local, national, and international politics. From policy decisions and election coverage to political analysis and key debates, our Politics section provides insightful reporting and in-depth coverage of the events shaping our world.','2024-12-23 17:55:45','2024-12-23 17:55:45'),(7,'Sports','A sports news website can feature real-time updates on matches, breaking news, player transfers, and expert analysis, accompanied by live scores and fixture schedules. It can include engaging content like match highlights, player profiles, fan polls, and photo galleries, offering a comprehensive experience for sports enthusiasts.','2024-12-23 17:55:50','2024-12-23 17:55:50'),(8,'Technology','A Technology News website provides the latest updates, insights, and developments in the world of technology. It covers a wide range of topics including gadgets, software, hardware, tech industry trends, innovations, product reviews, scientific breakthroughs, and emerging technologies like artificial intelligence, robotics, and blockchain. These websites aim to inform tech enthusiasts, professionals, and consumers about new technologies, innovations, and advancements, offering expert opinions, reviews, and discussions about their impact on society.','2024-12-23 17:55:54','2024-12-23 17:55:54'),(9,'Health','Stay informed with the latest updates on health and wellness. Our Health News section covers a wide range of topics, including medical breakthroughs, health tips, fitness advice, mental well-being, disease prevention, nutrition, and more. We bring you expert insights, trends, and in-depth reports to help you live a healthier life. Stay updated on the newest health studies and expert opinions for better decision-making about your health and lifestyle.','2024-12-23 17:55:58','2024-12-23 17:55:58'),(10,'Education','Stay informed with the latest updates, trends, and insights from the world of education. Our Education News section covers a wide range of topics including academic achievements, school reforms, educational policies, and innovations in teaching. We bring you news on the evolving educational landscape, the impact of technology in classrooms, and stories about students, teachers, and educational institutions from around the world. Whether it is breaking news on curriculum changes, scholarship opportunities, or tips for academic success, find all you need to know about education here.','2024-12-23 17:56:03','2024-12-23 17:56:03'),(11,'Science','A Science News website delivers the latest updates on scientific discoveries, research, and innovations across fields like biology, physics, astronomy, and technology. It features articles on groundbreaking studies, expert insights, and trending scientific topics such as climate change, space exploration, and medical advancements, making complex scientific developments accessible to a broad audience, from enthusiasts to professionals.','2024-12-23 17:56:08','2024-12-23 17:56:08'),(12,'Environment','Stay updated on the latest developments in environmental issues, climate change, sustainability, and conservation efforts. Our coverage includes global and local news on ecosystems, wildlife protection, renewable energy, pollution, and green innovations. We aim to keep you informed on how environmental challenges impact the world and the actions being taken to preserve our planet for future generations.','2024-12-23 17:56:12','2024-12-23 17:56:12');
